---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Duty of Care & Compliance | WasteWize UK"
  description="Your legal Waste Duty of Care explained. WasteWize issues waste transfer notes on every job. EA-licensed — protecting you from unlimited fines."
>

  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "name": "Duty of Care & Compliance | WasteWize UK",
      "url": "https://wastewize.co.uk/duty-of-care",
      "description": "Understanding your legal Waste Duty of Care obligations and how WasteWize UK ensures full compliance.",
      "breadcrumb": {
        "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
        "itemListElement": [
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home",          "item": "https://wastewize.co.uk/" },
          { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Duty of Care", "item": "https://wastewize.co.uk/duty-of-care" }
        ]
      }
    })} />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <nav class="bg-brand-dark border-b border-white/5 py-3 px-4" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-white/40">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-lime transition-colors">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-hidden="true">›</li>
        <li class="text-white/70">Duty of Care</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>

    <!-- ── Hero ── -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-brand-dark border-b border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-lime/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl relative z-10 text-center">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-lime block mb-3">
          Regulatory Compliance
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-5">
          Your <span class="text-brand-lime">Duty of Care</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Under Section 34 of the Environmental Protection Act 1990, anyone who produces waste has a legal duty to ensure it is disposed of responsibly — or face unlimited fines.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ── Three pillars ── -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-brand-dark">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

          <div class="group bg-brand-dark-card border border-white/10 rounded-[12px] p-6
                      flex flex-col gap-4 hover:border-brand-lime/50 hover:shadow-card
                      hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-[10px] bg-brand-lime/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0
                        group-hover:bg-brand-lime/20 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-lime" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">Full Indemnity</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">By using an Upper-Tier EA Licensed Carrier like WasteWize, the legal responsibility for the waste is safely transferred from you to us.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group bg-brand-dark-card border border-white/10 rounded-[12px] p-6
                      flex flex-col gap-4 hover:border-brand-lime/50 hover:shadow-card
                      hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-[10px] bg-brand-lime/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0
                        group-hover:bg-brand-lime/20 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-lime" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 2v-6m2 8V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">Waste Transfer Notes</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">Every collection is documented with a digital WTN, providing a permanent audit trail of where your waste originated and where it ended up.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group bg-brand-dark-card border border-white/10 rounded-[12px] p-6
                      flex flex-col gap-4 hover:border-brand-lime/50 hover:shadow-card
                      hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-[10px] bg-brand-lime/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0
                        group-hover:bg-brand-lime/20 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-lime" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">The Waste Hierarchy</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">We legally must prioritise the waste hierarchy: Prevent, Reuse, Recycle, Recover, and — only as a last resort — Dispose.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Why it matters ── -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-brand-dark-card border-y border-white/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-lime block mb-3">
          The Legal Risk
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Why Does This Matter to You?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-10">
          If your waste is fly-tipped by an unlicensed carrier, <strong class="text-white font-semibold">you</strong> are legally liable and can face unlimited fines or prosecution. Simply "paying someone to take it away" is not enough to satisfy the law.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-lime pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">For Homeowners</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">"I didn't know they were unlicensed" is not a legal defence. Using WasteWize UK ensures you have the paperwork to prove you acted responsibly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-lime pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">For Businesses</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">Commercial entities are required by law to keep Waste Transfer Notes for at least 2 years. Our digital system handles this archiving for you automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Digital WTN ── -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-brand-dark border-b border-white/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-14">

          <div class="flex-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-lime block mb-3">
              The Documentation
            </span>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-5">
              Digital Waste Transfer Notes (WTN)
            </h2>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Upon completion of every job, we issue a digital WTN. This document contains:
            </p>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
              {[
                'Description of the waste (SIC Codes)',
                'The volume and weight of the materials',
                'The date, time, and location of collection',
                'Our Environment Agency Licence Number',
                'The destination licensed site for material recovery',
              ].map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-white/70">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-lime shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Mock WTN Document -->
          <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-sm rotate-1">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden text-gray-800 text-[11px] font-sans select-none">

              <!-- Header band -->
              <div class="bg-[#1a2e1a] px-5 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-brand-lime font-bold text-[13px] tracking-tight">WasteWize UK</p>
                  <p class="text-white/50 text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">Licensed Waste Carrier</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                  <p class="text-white/40 text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">EA Licence</p>
                  <p class="text-brand-lime font-mono text-[11px] font-bold">CBDU335711</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Document title -->
              <div class="px-5 pt-4 pb-3 border-b border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-[13px] text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wide">Waste Transfer Note</h3>
                <div class="flex gap-4 mt-1 text-[9px] text-gray-400">
                  <span>Ref: <span class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">WW-2025-8821</span></span>
                  <span>Date: <span class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">11 May 2025</span></span>
                  <span>Time: <span class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">09:14</span></span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="px-5 py-3 space-y-3">

                <!-- Producer -->
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1">Waste Producer</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Acme Construction Ltd</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px]">47 Meridian Way, London, N1 3BT</p>
                </div>

                <div class="border-t border-gray-100"></div>

                <!-- Waste description -->
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1.5">Waste Description</p>
                  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-[10px]">
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-gray-400">SIC Code:</span>
                      <span class="ml-1 font-semibold text-gray-700">17 01 01</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-gray-400">Type:</span>
                      <span class="ml-1 font-semibold text-gray-700">Mixed C&amp;D</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-gray-400">Volume:</span>
                      <span class="ml-1 font-semibold text-gray-700">6 yd³</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-gray-400">Weight:</span>
                      <span class="ml-1 font-semibold text-gray-700">~850 kg</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="border-t border-gray-100"></div>

                <!-- Destination -->
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1">Destination Facility</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Veolia Recycling Centre</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px]">Smugglers Way, Wandsworth, SW18 1EQ</p>
                  <p class="text-[9px] mt-0.5">
                    <span class="text-gray-400">Permit:</span>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700 ml-0.5">EPR/AB3942LD</span>
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="border-t border-gray-100"></div>

                <!-- Hierarchy + recycling rate -->
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1">Waste Hierarchy</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-1">
                      {['Recycle', 'Recover'].map((tier) => (
                        <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-[8px] font-semibold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">
                          {tier}
                        </span>
                      ))}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-right">
                    <p class="text-[8px] text-gray-400">Diversion rate</p>
                    <p class="text-[20px] font-extrabold text-green-700 leading-none">99%</p>
                    <p class="text-[8px] text-gray-400">landfill-free</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

              </div>

              <!-- Footer / stamp -->
              <div class="bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200 px-5 py-2.5 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-2 h-2 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[9px] font-semibold text-green-700">Duty of Care Satisfied</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-[8px] text-gray-400 font-mono">DIGITALLY ISSUED · WasteWize UK</span>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-brand-dark">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center max-w-2xl">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-lime block mb-3">
          Get Compliant Today
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Need a Compliant Waste Partner?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Don't risk fines. Get a fully documented, professional waste collection today.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact#quote"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-brand-forest text-white
                   px-6 py-3 rounded-[8px] text-sm font-semibold
                   hover:bg-brand-forest-dark hover:-translate-y-px hover:shadow-cta
                   transition-all duration-200"
          >
            Get a Free Quote
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:+447929771954"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/15
                   text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-[8px] text-sm font-semibold
                   hover:border-brand-lime/50 hover:bg-white/10 hover:-translate-y-px
                   transition-all duration-200"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-lime" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z"/>
            </svg>
            07929 771954
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
